trans-unit.source: Defines endpoint or contract behaviors that can export custom metadata.
trans-unit.target: Definierar slutpunkt eller kontraktet beteenden som kan exportera anpassade metadata.

trans-unit.source: To modify and extend the Web Services Description Language (WSDL) exported by <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlExporter> objects, implement the IWsdlExportExtension interface on an endpoint, contract, or operation behavior (an object that implements either <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.IContractBehavior>, <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.IEndpointBehavior>, or <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.IOperationBehavior>) and add the behavior to the <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.ServiceEndpoint.Behaviors%2A>, <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.ContractDescription.Behaviors%2A>, or <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.OperationDescription.Behaviors%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: Att ändra och utöka de Web Services WSDL (Description Language) exporteras av <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlExporter>objekt, implementera gränssnittet IWsdlExportExtension på en slutpunkt, kontrakt eller åtgärden beteende (ett objekt som implementerar antingen <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.IContractBehavior>, <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.IEndpointBehavior>, eller <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.IOperationBehavior>) och lägga till funktionen för att den <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.ServiceEndpoint.Behaviors%2A>, <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.ContractDescription.Behaviors%2A>, eller <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.OperationDescription.Behaviors%2A>egenskap.</xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.OperationDescription.Behaviors%2A> </xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.ContractDescription.Behaviors%2A> </xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.ServiceEndpoint.Behaviors%2A> </xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.IOperationBehavior> </xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.IEndpointBehavior> </xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.IContractBehavior> </xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlExporter>

trans-unit.source: In addition, you can also implement IWsdlExportExtension on a <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.BindingElement>.
trans-unit.target: Du kan dessutom också implementera IWsdlExportExtension <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.BindingElement>.</xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.BindingElement>

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > IWsdlExportExtension implementations are never invoked if they are implemented as an <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.IServiceBehavior>.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > IWsdlExportExtension implementeringar aldrig anropas om de har implementerats som en <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.IServiceBehavior>.</xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.IServiceBehavior>

trans-unit.source: IWsdlExportExtension does not export custom policy assertions even though [!INCLUDE[indigo1](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] exports custom binding policy assertions to the appropriate element inside WSDL.
trans-unit.target: IWsdlExportExtension exporterar inte anpassade principkontroller även om [!INCLUDE[indigo1](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] exporterar anpassade bindningen principkontroller till lämplig elementet i WSDL.

trans-unit.source: If you want to export custom policy assertions, implement the <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.IPolicyExportExtension> interface.
trans-unit.target: Om du vill exportera anpassade principkontroller implementerar den <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.IPolicyExportExtension>gränssnitt.</xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.IPolicyExportExtension>

trans-unit.source: The metadata publication process begins by calling <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlExporter.ExportEndpoints%2A?displayProperty=fullName> which in turn calls <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlExporter.ExportEndpoint%2A?displayProperty=fullName> for each endpoint.
trans-unit.target: Metadata för publikationen börjar genom att anropa <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlExporter.ExportEndpoints%2A?displayProperty=fullName>som i sin tur anropar <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlExporter.ExportEndpoint%2A?displayProperty=fullName>för varje slutpunkt.</xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlExporter.ExportEndpoint%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlExporter.ExportEndpoints%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: The endpoint is exported by first exporting its contract.When exporting a contract the <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlExporter?displayProperty=fullName> calls the <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.IWsdlExportExtension.ExportContract%2A?displayProperty=fullName> method on all IWsdlExportExtension implementations on the contract, and operation behaviors for that contract.
trans-unit.target: Slutpunkten exporteras genom att först exportera dess kontrakt. När du exporterar ett kontrakt i <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlExporter?displayProperty=fullName>anrop av <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.IWsdlExportExtension.ExportContract%2A?displayProperty=fullName>metoden på alla IWsdlExportExtension implementeringar i kontrakt och åtgärd beteenden för kontraktet.</xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.IWsdlExportExtension.ExportContract%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlExporter?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: Operations that use wildcard actions are not exported in metadata, so IWsdlExportExtension implementations on operation behaviors for these operations are not exported.
trans-unit.target: Åtgärder som använder jokertecken åtgärder exporteras inte i metadata, så IWsdlExportExtension implementeringar på åtgärden beteenden för dessa åtgärder inte exporteras.

trans-unit.source: After exporting the contract, the port and binding are exported and exported policy expressions are attached.
trans-unit.target: När du exporterar kontraktet porten och bindningen exporteras och exportera princip uttryck är anslutna.

trans-unit.source: Both the <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.IWsdlExportExtension.ExportContract%2A> and the <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.IWsdlExportExtension.ExportEndpoint%2A> methods provide access to the <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlExporter> so that IWsdlExportExtension implementations can report recoverable errors and warnings through the <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.MetadataExporter.Errors%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: Både den <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.IWsdlExportExtension.ExportContract%2A>och <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.IWsdlExportExtension.ExportEndpoint%2A>metoder ger åtkomst till den <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlExporter>så att IWsdlExportExtension implementeringar kan rapportera fel och varningar via den <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.MetadataExporter.Errors%2A>egenskapen.</xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.MetadataExporter.Errors%2A> </xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlExporter> </xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.IWsdlExportExtension.ExportEndpoint%2A> </xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.IWsdlExportExtension.ExportContract%2A>

trans-unit.source: The context objects passed into both methods provide convenient mappings from exported WSDL elements to properties of <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.ContractDescription> and <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.ServiceEndpoint> objects.
trans-unit.target: Kontextobjekt som skickades till båda metoderna ger praktiska mappningar från den exporterade WSDL element till egenskaperna för <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.ContractDescription>och <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.ServiceEndpoint>objekt.</xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.ServiceEndpoint> </xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.ContractDescription>

trans-unit.source: If an IWsdlExportExtension implementation throws an exception on export, the generated metadata is in an inconsistent state and the <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlExporter> object should be discarded.
trans-unit.target: Om en IWsdlExportExtension implementering genererar ett undantag vid export, genererade metadata är i ett inkonsekvent tillstånd och <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlExporter>objektet bör kasseras.</xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlExporter>

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > Custom export extension must run after the built-in serializer populates the service description.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > Tillägget för anpassat export måste köras efter inbyggda serialiseraren fyller tjänstebeskrivningen.

trans-unit.source: Writes custom Web Services Description Language (WSDL) elements into the generated WSDL for a contract.
trans-unit.target: Skriver egna Web Services WSDL (Description Language)-element i den genererade WSDL för ett kontrakt.

trans-unit.source: The ExportContract method is called when the metadata export system is exporting the contract.
trans-unit.target: ExportContract-metoden anropas när metadata export system exporterar kontraktet.

trans-unit.source: Only contract and operation behaviors implementing <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.IWsdlExportExtension> get the ExportContract call.
trans-unit.target: Endast kontrakt och åtgärd beteenden som implementerar <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.IWsdlExportExtension>ExportContract samtalet.</xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.IWsdlExportExtension>

trans-unit.source: All behaviors implementing <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.IWsdlExportExtension> get the <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.IWsdlExportExtension.ExportEndpoint%2A> call.
trans-unit.target: Alla beteenden implementera <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.IWsdlExportExtension>Hämta den <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.IWsdlExportExtension.ExportEndpoint%2A>anropa.</xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.IWsdlExportExtension.ExportEndpoint%2A> </xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.IWsdlExportExtension>

trans-unit.source: Use the `context` parameter to modify the WSDL to be exported.
trans-unit.target: Använd den `context` parametern för att ändra WSDL exporteras.

trans-unit.source: For an example, see the Example section.
trans-unit.target: Ett exempel finns i avsnittet exempel.

trans-unit.source: The <xref href="System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlExporter"></xref> that exports the contract information.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref href="System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlExporter"> </xref> som exporterar kontraktsinformation.

trans-unit.source: Provides mappings from exported WSDL elements to the contract description.
trans-unit.target: Innehåller mappningar från exporterade WSDL-element i kontraktet beskrivningen.

trans-unit.source: Writes custom Web Services Description Language (WSDL) elements into the generated WSDL for an endpoint.
trans-unit.target: Skriver egna Web Services WSDL (Description Language)-element i den genererade WSDL för en slutpunkt.

trans-unit.source: Implement the ExportEndpoint method to modify the WSDL exported for an endpoint.
trans-unit.target: Implementera metoden ExportEndpoint om du vill ändra WSDL exporteras för en slutpunkt.

trans-unit.source: This method is called after the contract has been exported by <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.IWsdlExportExtension.ExportContract%2A>.
trans-unit.target: Den här metoden anropas när kontraktet har exporterats av <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.IWsdlExportExtension.ExportContract%2A>.</xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.IWsdlExportExtension.ExportContract%2A>

trans-unit.source: The <xref href="System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlExporter"></xref> that exports the endpoint information.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref href="System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlExporter"> </xref> som exporterar endpoint-information.

trans-unit.source: Provides mappings from exported WSDL elements to the endpoint description.
trans-unit.target: Innehåller mappningar från exporterade WSDL-element för slutpunkt-beskrivningen.
